This repository contains a ShowOff presentation for "The Why of Ruby" TechTalk given at JWM Solutions.

To serve the presentation install

  $ gem install showoff

And from the root directory execute

  $ showoff serve

You can modify the slides at the .md files.

-- 

Audience:
  Executive

Objective:

  Introduce the Ruby language as an innovate technology.

  Show how some companies have reached bussiness success by using
  new technologies and encouraging people to create them. 

  Share some lessons of the benefits a company can have from
  opensourcing software.

  Motivate developers to learn more languages and become better
  and more passionate about what they do.

An static version of this can be seen at 

  http://vic.github.com/jwm-tt-why-ruby
